title: You Don't Need Permission To Be Great, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO26
description: Who needs to validate you? Who needs to approve of your business idea?  No one but person looking at you in the mirror every morning.  In this Thursday Thunder edition of the MFCEO Project, Andy Frisella shoots it straight: You don't need permission to be great.
